songs.title: Birdman’s Tattoos
songs.lyrics:
A body map of Birdman's tattoos, starting from the top-right, working down to bottom-left



Head

Five red stars

Right face

Left Face

"Rich Gang"

Neck

Chest

Ball Till U Fall
Lil Wayne's face
Bang Bang

Stomach

Back

Right arm

Left arm

VL

Right hand
YMCMYSL
Rich G
Left hand

Right leg

Left leg
